main event: A vehicle with multiple observers spotted a possible large vehicle in the sky on December 25.
interesting points: The object was observed at an altitude of 4.7 miles.
The object was sighted between 17:00 and 17:05.
The object was described as a clear, flat, round, white object that was moving very fast northbound.
The object was estimated to be 2-3 feet in diameter.
The sighting occurred in the Montexcity area.
